data.description: Updated 4 bedroom, 2.5 half bath home with fully fenced backyard in Center Grove Schools. Main level has 2 spacious gathering locations perfect for entertaining with newer vinyl plank flooring.  First is the Living Room connected to formal Dining Room. The second is the Great Room with gas log fireplace open to the 2nd dining area and kitchen with lots of counter/cabinet space. Primary bedroom suite with french door entry, vaulted ceiling and bathroom with dual vanities, easy step-in tiled shower and walk-in closet. The 4th bedroom or Bonus Room is HUGE with vaulted ceiling. It is actually much bigger than primary bedroom. It doesn't have a closet but seller is leaving full sized armoire for clothing storage or use it as a work out room, game room or office. Backyard features a large wood deck, privacy fence and mature trees. Updates include Roof & Kitchen Counter-tops in 2018, Fireplace insert in 2019, Water Softener in 2020 and all of the following in last 2 years vinyl plank flooring, shower in hall bath, refrigerator, dishwasher, washer, dryer, and even the water heater.
